# Exercise 10: Check Link Count

### Create new file

```bash
echo "Link Count Demo" > file3.txt
```

### View link count

```bash
ls -li file3.txt
```

### Create two hard links

```bash
ln file3.txt hard1.txt
ln file3.txt hard2.txt
```

### Verify

```bash
ls -li
```

### Observation

Link count increases from:

```text
1 → 3
```

### Explanation

There are now 3 filenames pointing to the same inode.

