# Exercise 11: Soft Link to a Directory

### Create directory

```bash
mkdir project
```

### Create soft link

```bash
ln -s project project_link
```

### Verify

```bash
ls -l
```

### Navigate

```bash
cd project_link
pwd
```

### Result

✔ Soft links can be created for directories.

---

# Exercise 12: Hard Link Limitation

### Try creating hard link for directory

```bash
ln project project_hardlink
```

### Expected Output

```text
ln: project: hard link not allowed for directory
```

### Result

✔ Hard links cannot normally be created for directories.

